<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 12:20:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>台湾扩大对俄罗斯的制裁，以阻止技术被用于武器</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-expands-russian-sanctions-stop-tech-being-used-arms-2023-12-26/</link><description>台湾经济部周二表示，针对俄罗斯入侵乌克兰，扩大了对俄罗斯及其盟友白俄罗斯的制裁商品清单，以防止台湾高科技产品被用于军事目的。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 11:31:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-expands-russian-sanctions-stop-tech-being-used-arms-2023-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>进入 2024 年，美国行业整合增强了大型石油公司的实力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/big-oil-enters-2024-strengthened-by-us-industry-consolidation-2023-12-26/</link><description>石油和天然气行业在 2023 年进行了 2500 亿美元的收购热潮，利用公司的高股价来获得较低成本的储备，并为可能经历更多整合的行业的下一次剧变做好准备。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 11:02:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/big-oil-enters-2024-strengthened-by-us-industry-consolidation-2023-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统候选人指责反对党“亲共”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-presidential-frontrunner-accuses-opposition-party-being-pro-communist-2023-12-26/</link><description>台湾下一任总统的领跑者在下个月的选举前指责主要反对党背叛了其先辈的反共理想并公开支持中国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 09:20:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-presidential-frontrunner-accuses-opposition-party-being-pro-communist-2023-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国严厉打击数亿美元政府投资诈骗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cracks-down-hundreds-millions-dollars-government-investment-scams-2023-12-26/</link><description>据官方媒体周二报道，中国警方今年破获了利用伪造政府文件吸引虚假国家项目投资的数亿美元诈骗案件。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 08:47:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cracks-down-hundreds-millions-dollars-government-investment-scams-2023-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>阿斯利康斥资12亿美元收购中国亘喜生物</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/aztrazeneca-buy-china-based-gracell-biotechnologies-12-bln-deal-2023-12-26/</link><description>阿斯利康周二表示，将以高达 12 亿美元的价格收购 Gracell Biotechnologies，这家英瑞制药公司将进一步推进其细胞治疗雄心，并增强其在全球第二大制药市场中国的业务。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 07:13:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/aztrazeneca-buy-china-based-gracell-biotechnologies-12-bln-deal-2023-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>监管举措令投资者不安后，中国游戏公司宣布股票回购</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-gaming-firms-unveil-share-buybacks-after-regulatory-move-unnerves-2023-12-26/</link><description>许多规模较小的中国游戏公司宣布了股票回购计划，这些计划被视为在市场因打击消费者游戏支出的监管举措而受到惊吓后试图安抚投资者。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 05:49:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-gaming-firms-unveil-share-buybacks-after-regulatory-move-unnerves-2023-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾军方称菲律宾并未挑起南海冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-not-provoking-conflict-south-china-sea-military-spokesperson-2023-12-26/</link><description>菲律宾军方发言人周二表示，菲律宾没有挑起南海冲突，回应中国有关马尼拉侵犯北京领土的指控。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 05:14:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-not-provoking-conflict-south-china-sea-military-spokesperson-2023-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>预计2024年中国将出现酷暑和更多极端天气</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-expects-searing-heat-more-weather-extremes-2024-2023-12-26/</link><description>一位高级气候专家表示，中国正在努力应对有记录以来最冷的12月，明年由于厄尔尼诺天气现象，中国可能不得不迎接另一轮酷暑和极端天气的增加。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 04:49:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-expects-searing-heat-more-weather-extremes-2024-2023-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>台湾选举前没有看到中国大规模军事活动的迹象</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-not-seeing-signs-large-scale-chinese-military-activity-pre-election-2023-12-26/</link><description>台湾国防部周二表示，在下个月的选举之前，台湾没有看到任何中国大规模军事活动的迹象，但正在密切关注中国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 04:07:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-not-seeing-signs-large-scale-chinese-military-activity-pre-election-2023-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国警告火箭弹残骸将袭击南海</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-warns-rocket-remnants-hit-south-china-sea-maritime-safety-authority-2023-12-26/</link><description>中国警告说，继十一天前第六次部署其最强大的运载火箭后，一枚火箭的残余物将于周二击中南海的一个地区。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 01:39:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-warns-rocket-remnants-hit-south-china-sea-maritime-safety-authority-2023-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国将为在印度被捕的vivo员工提供领事协助</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/china-provide-consular-assistance-vivo-employees-arrested-india-2023-12-25/</link><description>外交部发言人周一表示，中方将为印度当局逮捕的智能手机制造商 Vivo 两名中国员工提供领事保护和协助，并敦促印方不要歧视中国企业。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 08:59:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/china-provide-consular-assistance-vivo-employees-arrested-india-2023-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国的圣诞节充满了闪闪发光的装饰和外国影响的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/christmas-china-brings-glittering-decor-foreign-influence-concerns-2023-12-25/</link><description>在中国大城市金光闪闪的商场里，装饰着灯光、金属丝和礼品盒的巨型圣诞树迎接着购物者，但在中国的许多地方，延长节日的问候是不可能的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 05:30:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/christmas-china-brings-glittering-decor-foreign-influence-concerns-2023-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国官方媒体：菲律宾在南海的行动“极其危险”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-actions-south-china-sea-extremely-dangerous-chinese-state-media-2023-12-25/</link><description>中国官方媒体周一指责菲律宾多次侵犯中国在南海的领土、散布虚假信息并勾结域外势力滋事。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 01:52:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-actions-south-china-sea-extremely-dangerous-chinese-state-media-2023-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国地震死亡人数上升至149人，一周后仍有两人失踪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-earthquake-death-toll-rises-149-two-still-missing-after-week-2023-12-25/</link><description>中国近年来最强烈的地震之一横跨甘肃省和青海省，该地区居住着许多中国回族（一个紧密团结的少数民族）。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 00:28:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-earthquake-death-toll-rises-149-two-still-missing-after-week-2023-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>北京打破七十年来的寒冷天气记录</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-henan-province-hit-by-shortage-winter-heating-after-cold-wave-2023-12-24/</link><description>由于来自北极的刺骨冷空气，东北部部分地区气温达到-40摄氏度和华氏度。自12月11日以来，北京气象台记录了超过300小时的零下气温。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Dec 2023 06:56:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-henan-province-hit-by-shortage-winter-heating-after-cold-wave-2023-12-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>